trans-unit.source: Indicates that the .NET Framework class library method to which this attribute is applied is unlikely to be affected by servicing releases, and therefore is eligible to be inlined across Native Image Generator (NGen) images.
trans-unit.target: 表示套用此屬性的 .NET Framework Class Library 方法不會受到服務版本的影響，因此可以內嵌在原生影像產生器 (Native Image Generator，NGen) 的影像中。

trans-unit.source: The reason why the method to which the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.TargetedPatchingOptOutAttribute" /> attribute is applied is considered to be eligible for inlining across Native Image Generator (NGen) images.
trans-unit.target: 將套用了 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.TargetedPatchingOptOutAttribute" /> 屬性的方法視為符合資格，且可內嵌在不同原生影像產生器 (Native Image Generator，NGen) 影像中的原因。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.TargetedPatchingOptOutAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.TargetedPatchingOptOutAttribute" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the reason why the method to which this attribute is applied is considered to be eligible for inlining across Native Image Generator (NGen) images.
trans-unit.target: 取得原因，該原因可說明為什麼套用此屬性的方法被視為符合資格，而且可以內嵌在不同原生影像產生器 (Native Image Generator，NGen) 影像中。

trans-unit.source: The reason why the method is considered to be eligible for inlining across NGen images.
trans-unit.target: 視此方法為符合資格，且可內嵌在不同原生影像產生器影像中的原因。
